description: Contains some simple and commonly used WPF controls based on HandyControl
releaseNotes:
https://github.com/HandyOrg/HandyControl/issues/748 NotifyIcon support for windows-less mode
Grid support for named RowDefinitions and ColumnDefinitions
Improved BlurWindow, more versions of system are supported
growl support for 'Default Panel', you don't need to set hc:Growl.GrowlParent="True"
PropertyGrid support for custom editors
optimized InfoElement.Title style
https://github.com/HandyOrg/HandyControl/issues/795 scrollbar support for always-visible mode
https://github.com/HandyOrg/HandyControl/issues/516 support for InputGroup

Add Force_Enable_Acrylic_Blur Property for BlurWindow
Add PersianDatePicker ConfirmButtonText Property
Add UpdatableMarkupExtensions
Support Afghanistan Month Name in Calendar
memory optimization
ProgressBar style updated
hc styles can be referenced in window.resource
Fixed ColorPicker Issue
Fixed Shield ContentStringFormat not work
Fixed Loading canâ€˜t pause when IsRunning prop is assigned to false
Fixed some value are not cleared when the clear button is clicked
